title: Huge photoshop brushes collection
description:
Thousands of brushes all set together on a torrent. I kept the whole morning downloading various brushes. Credits goes to each and every owner of the brushes. Enjoy!


How to install:

-Unzip the downloaded file, if necessary.

-Move the unzipped .abr brush file to the Photoshop brushes presets folder on your hard drive. For a Mac, the path is Finder > Applications > Adobe Photoshop > Presets > Brushes. For a PC, the path is Program Files > Adobe > Photoshop > Presets > Brushes.

-Open Photoshop.

-Go to brushes

-Press Load Brushes

-Find your brush set

Note: Once you load, you wont have to load again.
